                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>In a newspaper interview granted September 3, 1951, Mr. Dulles
                                replied to certain assertions made by the Government of the U.S.S.R.
                                regarding the preparation and content of the Japanese Peace Treaty.
                                For text, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>,
                                September 17, 1951, page 461.</p>
                        </div>
